headline: Homes.com Report: Home Price Increases Slowed for the Fourth Consecutive Month in April
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., May 14, 2025--Homes.com, a CoStar Group leading online residential marketplace, today released a new report analyzing home prices in April (based on the data collected to date), price trends across major metros, and what the latest developments in the housing market mean for homebuyers.
